      "content": "everything is just... empty. i've spent so long looking for some kind of objective purpose or a reason to keep grinding through this, but there's nothing. just physics and entropy. it feels like we're just biological accidents waiting to decay. there's no light at the end of the tunnel, just more darkness.",
