      "content": "it's just exhausting. the idea that the \"honest\" thing to do is just to sit here and wait for the decay... it makes everything feel so heavy. like, if there's no point to the struggle, why keep fighting against the darkness? it feels like everyone is just fighting a losing battle against a void that doesn't even care.",
